snippet.title: Exfil  Pre-Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/860020/Exfil/
Discord: https://discord.gg/xG5GVKQ
Web: http://misultin.com

EXFIL is a multiplayer game where strategy, communication, and adaptability are key. Two teams compete to recover crucial intel and make an escape, all while trying to outsmart and outmaneuver their opponents.
